265
00:19:41.723 --> 00:19:43.349
<i>Pull yourself together, Yoon Bom.</i>

266
00:19:43.433 --> 00:19:46.227
<i>If the students find out, you're done for.</i>

267
00:19:46.311 --> 00:19:49.314
<i>When you see Mr. Sun today,</i>
<i>you need to be completely hostile</i>

268
00:19:49.397 --> 00:19:50.899
