00:25:28.819 --> 00:25:30.947
Sir, we're coming in.

334
00:25:55.221 --> 00:25:56.222
Hello.

335
00:25:56.806 --> 00:26:00.101
We're from the Green Narae Energy Club
at Shinsu High.

