00:26:51.027 --> 00:26:51.986
Hello.

338
00:26:52.737 --> 00:26:56.574
I'm Sun Jae-gyu, CEO of JQ Energy.

339
00:26:59.577 --> 00:27:00.494
Your uncle is...

340
00:27:02.663 --> 00:27:03.831
