376
00:29:30.811 --> 00:29:34.273
So he talks all smooth
in a Seoul accent while smiling at you.

377
00:29:34.356 --> 00:29:36.859
You think that means
he's into you or something?

378
00:29:37.610 --> 00:29:40.488
